t_news_breaking_audio::clip_card_1::goal: Deebii gochaa namoota taatechi tuqee waraabi.
t_news_breaking_audio::clip_card_5::goal: Bu'aa waan mudatee sirriitti kan mul'isu waraabi.
t_news_breaking_audio::ms_moreinfo::head: Itti Aanee
t_news_breaking_audio::clip_card_4::goal: Yoo danda'ame, bakkichatti nama miidhameef gaafannoo geggeessi.
t_news_breaking_audio::title: Gabaasa Sagalee Oduu Tasaa
t_news_breaking_audio::text_card_0::text: Gabaasi sagalee oduu tasaa sagalee kan waan mudate ibsu, qabxii ijoo cuunfu, qaama qooda fudhatee fi odeeffannoo hamma yerichaatti argame hunda barbaada. Gabaasaan bakka mudannichaatti waan argamu ibsuu qaba. Sagalee haqa bu'uuraa dhiyeessuu fi yoo danda'ame namoota arganiif gaaffiif deebii geggeessee dhiyeessuu waraabi
